         Ok, I have a list in front of me of words and I have made everyone of these (ahead of time) for lvl 34.  I do have a question though, but that can wait... first the spells and words to go with them for lvl 34 necro...</P><P><b>Invoke Fear: words of resolve, quivering, and duration.<BR>Call of Bones (pet): Words of Motion, Neglect, and Endurance.<BR>Wave of Enfeeblement: Words of Abatement, Caz-Thule, and Efficacy.<BR>Invoke Shadow : Words of Dark Paths, Haunting, and Suffering.</b></P><P>Now, according to two different sites, one of them being castersrealm.com there is a lvl 44 spell called Beguile, which is research.  The closest thing any necro has been able to tell me about it is that it is <b>Beguile Undead</b> and is a lvl 34 spell.  The words for it are Enchantment and Subordination.  And apparently you can purchase it.</P><P>Does anyone know about this?  <b>IS</b> there another beguile spell that is for necros, not the enchanter one?</P><P>Thanks for your help and I hope I've been helpful.</P><P>Knowledge is only outdone by stupidity.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
