         I second the vote on Vendor Mining!</P><P>For spells, I mine the vendors at the necro/SK guilds in cities first, then the other caster guilds second -- If I sell a spell I've made using research, I always put it there.  (e.g. Echo Caverns on Luclin, Cabilis, etc.)</P><P>For words, I've had the best luck mining:<ul><li>Non-caster guilds anywhere</li><li>Caster guilds of non-KOS cities without necro/sk guilds -- e.g. Bazaar, Shar Val, Shadowhaven, Thurgadin, etc.</li></ul></P><P></P><P>Edited by - Gunkk on 07/23/2002  10:06:29<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
