        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Ok I'll share the knowledge I've come across so far in my career.</P><P>At the Treant camp in SK where I lived from 24 to 34 they used to drop the 16-24th words and runes for the INT classes.</P><P>In DL the various mobs in zone dropped all the 34-39 words and runes for the INT classes.</P><P>In SF the various mobs drops the 34-49 words and runes for the INT classes as well as various drop only spells for 50+.</P><P>I know I have a gap in the lvl range 29th words and runes (Marus Seru on Luclin springs to mind but I'm not sure they drop ALL the 29th words and runes) but I simply can't remember everything sorry.</P><P>Hope this helps a little:)</P><P>Moradonnar Soulforger 51st Vicar of Brell<BR>Shinshee Dreadmistress 51st Heretic of Lord Cazic</P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
