         I've found every word for every spell 16 to 29 in lake of ill omen. I have a current list of words in my inventory, and what spells they make. It's all in a nice online table. I'm working on making it customizable per user, but that's still off in the distance a little.</P><P>I also look for words at every vendor I stop at. I found the druid vendor in Lavastorm had some of the higher level spells, dropped in Sol B I guess.</P><P>The best time to check vendors for spells is about 8 hours after a patch, the inventory has been cleared making room for new items to show up, and you've given people time to hunt and sell.</P><P><u><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=305393" target="_blank">Look under Mraak's robe</a></u><BR>29th Lvl Death Priest of Cazic Thule<BR>Bertox<BR><u><a href="http://www.cox-internet.com/stormfire/" target="_blank">News, Tools, Humor</a></u><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
